guardian-selector-window-title = Holoparasite selection
guardian-selector-list-title = Available holoparasites
guardian-selector-confirm = Confirm
guardian-selector-no-selection = No holoparasite selected
guardian-selector-no-options = This injector has no holoparasite profiles loaded.
guardian-selector-not-held = You need to hold the injector to finish the injection.

guardian-selector-standard-name = Standard
guardian-selector-standard-description = Brutal armor-piercing punches, low damage transfer, and a configurable battle cry.
guardian-selector-standard-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: 30 armor-piercing blunt damage and 100 structural damage.
    - Damage transfer: 0.4 to the host.
    - Link range: 10 tiles.
    Battle cry:
    - Automatically shouts a custom cry while punching. Default: ORA. Maximum length: 8 characters.
    Fear aura:
    - All enemies within a 2-tile radius are significantly slowed.

guardian-selector-assassin-name = Assassin
guardian-selector-assassin-description = Stealthy movement, high melee damage, and full damage transfer to the host.
guardian-selector-assassin-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: 30 blunt damage and 5 poison damage.
    - Damage transfer: 0.8 to the host.
    - Link range: 10 tiles.
    Stealth:
    - Becomes difficult to see while moving carefully, then opens fights with a high-damage strike.
    Venom blades:
    - Every hit injects a toxin. Fragile for the host, so disengage quickly after striking.

guardian-selector-chaos-name = Chaos
guardian-selector-chaos-description = Burning melee attacks and unstable high-risk damage transfer.
guardian-selector-chaos-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: 15 armor-piercing heat damage and 20 structural damage.
    - Damage transfer: 0.6 to the host.
    - Link range: 10 tiles.
    Volatile strikes:
    - Melee hits can ignite targets, forcing them to extinguish themselves instead of fighting.
    Chaos profile:
    - Once every 10 seconds, can attract everyone nearby by striking any location.

guardian-selector-charger-name = Charger
guardian-selector-charger-description = Extreme speed, fast attacks, and a short-cooldown charge leap.
guardian-selector-charger-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: 15 armor-piercing blunt damage and 20 structural damage.
    - Damage transfer: 0.6 to the host.
    - Link range: 10 tiles.
    Charge:
    - Use the charge action to leap forward in the direction you are facing. Impact knocks targets down without disarming them.

guardian-selector-lightning-name = Lightning
guardian-selector-lightning-description = A defensive tesla link that protects the host and burns enemies crossing the arc.
guardian-selector-lightning-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: 18 shock damage and 20 structural damage.
    - Damage transfer: 0.5 to the host.
    - Link range: 8 tiles.
    Tesla link:
    - While the guardian exists, the host is protected from shock damage.
    - While manifested, a lightning arc links guardian and host. Mobs on the arc and nearby take 3 heat damage every 0.1 seconds.

guardian-selector-ice-name = Ice
guardian-selector-ice-description = Freezing melee strikes that sap stamina and chill targets.
guardian-selector-ice-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: 30 cold damage and 20 structural damage.
    - Damage transfer: 0.6 to the host.
    - Link range: 10 tiles.
    Frostbite:
    - Hits rapidly pull heat out of targets and deal light stamina damage.

guardian-selector-protector-name = Protector
guardian-selector-protector-description = Defensive guardian with an extended tether range.
guardian-selector-protector-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: 20 armor-piercing blunt damage and 20 structural damage.
    - Damage transfer: 0.3 to the host.
    - Link range: 15 tiles.
    Force wall:
    - Can create a short-lived magical barrier (the host cannot pass through it).

guardian-selector-ranged-name = Ranged
guardian-selector-ranged-description = Fragile guardian with rapid armor-piercing hard-light bolts.
guardian-selector-ranged-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: 10 armor-piercing blunt damage and 10 structural damage.
    - Damage transfer: 1.0 to the host.
    - Link range: 13 tiles.
    Hard-light bolt:
    - Use the targeted-ability key (default: MMB) to fire rapid armor-piercing bolts. Cooldown: 0.6 seconds.

guardian-selector-dexterous-name = Dexterous
guardian-selector-dexterous-description = Low damage, but can manipulate equipment with hands.
guardian-selector-dexterous-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: 10 blunt damage.
    - Damage transfer: 0.67 to the host.
    - Link range: 12 tiles.
    Dexterity:
    - Has hands, inventory, and complex interactions.

guardian-selector-support-name = Support
guardian-selector-support-description = Toxic melee strikes with a short-cooldown healing bolt.
guardian-selector-support-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: 5 blunt damage and 15 poison damage.
    - Damage transfer: 0.7 to the host.
    - Link range: 10 tiles.
    Healing bolt:
    - Use the targeted-ability key (default: MMB) to fire a small healing projectile. Cooldown: 2 seconds.

guardian-selector-healer-name = Healer
guardian-selector-healer-description = Slower, frailer guardian that heals instead of dealing melee damage.
guardian-selector-healer-details =
    Stats:
    - Melee: heals 5 brute, burn, airloss, and toxin damage instead of harming.
    - Damage transfer: 0.8 to the host.
    - Link range: 10 tiles.
    Healing bolt:
    - Use the targeted-ability key (default: MMB) to heal at range. Cooldown: 2 seconds.

guardian-evict-success = Your guardian's pilot has been forced out.
guardian-evict-empty = Nobody is currently piloting your guardian.
guardian-evict-failed = Your guardian's pilot could not be forced out.
